summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue additional Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Madison Street, from Thirty-third Avenue North to East Mercer Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 14985, creating Local Improvement District No. 1339 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
